Module org.apache.jena.arq
Package org.apache.jena.sparql.algebra

Class TransformSingle

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.sparql.algebra.TransformSingle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Transform
public class TransformSingle extends Object implements Transform
Special purpose base class for a single transformation. When writing Transforms to be applied to a tree, extend TransformCopy, not this class.
